{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"494","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"台積電降低供應鏈風險 鼓勵供應商分散生產","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>2019-07-13 17:06</span><span style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>中央社 記者張建中新竹<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;'>13</span>日電</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>日本加強管制<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;'>3</span>項關鍵電子材料出口南韓，可能重創南韓半導體與面板產業，引發各界對供應鏈風險的重視。台積電為降低供應鏈風險，鼓勵供應商分散生產廠區。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>日本與南韓因前徵用工爭議關係惡化，日本政府自<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;'>4</span>日起加強管制含氟聚醯亞胺（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;'>Fluorine Polyimide</span>）、光阻劑及蝕刻氣體（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;'>Etching Gas</span>）<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;'>3</span>項關鍵電子材料出口南韓。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>業界人士認為，日本管制的<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;'>3</span>項材料是半導體與面板廠不可或缺的關鍵材料，且短期要取得替代品很困難，日韓雙方關係若無法緩解，南韓三星<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;'>(Samsung)</span>、<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;'>SK</span>海力士（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;'>SK Hynix</span>）及<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;'>LG</span>等營運恐將遭受衝擊。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>隨著國際間貿易紛爭頻傳，供應鏈風險管理的重要性日益升高。台積電認為，除貿易緊張外，原料產地發生重大天災、政治或經濟動盪也都可能影響原物料取得或價格上漲。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>一旦無法適時取得充足的必要原物料，或原物料價格顯著上漲，增加的成本卻無法轉嫁給客戶，台積電認為，營收與獲利將可能因而下滑。包括矽晶圓、製程用氣體、化學原料及光阻劑等是台積電生產的關鍵原物料。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>為降低供應鏈中斷風險，台積電內部由晶圓廠、資材管理、風險管理以及品質管理等單位組成工作小組，協助供應商針對可能的潛在風險，訂定營運持續計畫，提升供應鏈的風險抵禦能力。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>除鼓勵供應商分散生產廠區，台積電也致力開發新供應商，降低供應鏈風險；台積電還鼓勵供應商將生產廠區自高成本地區移至台灣，提高成本競爭力。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>為有效管理供應鏈風險，台積電加強供應商的現場稽核與會議共識，並不斷改善庫存監控系統，提高需求預測的準確度，確保供應鏈維持足夠庫存水位。因供應鏈風險管理得宜，台積電去年並未有供應鏈中斷的情況。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;'>: https://money.udn.com/money/story/5612/3926990</span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2019-07-15","clk_count":"159"}},"__N_SSG":true}